<refsect1 id="XS-U-2a">
<title>Preliminaries</title>
<para> This sample program demonstrates the use of parameters in an updategram:</para>

<itemizedlist mark="bullet">
  <listitem>Create a form that allows new records to be inserted into a table.</listitem>
  <listitem>Use the form text fields as input parameters for the updategram.</listitem> 
  <listitem>After insert display a list of records to show that new record has been inserted into the table.</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</refsect1>
